{{!--
  "Compressed from" / "Compressed reading" pedagogy line.
  Lightweight one-line surface that reinforces the
  glossary §composition "Structural compression" concept directly on
  flagship trick-detail pages.

  Renders ONLY when the curator has explicitly allowlisted the slug in
  FAMOUS_COMPRESSION_SLUGS in freestyleService.ts (smear, ripwalk,
  atom-smasher, eggbeater, mobius). The view-model field
  content.compressedFrom is null for every other slug; this partial
  collapses cleanly with no output.

  Doctrine: pedagogy reinforcement, not ontology expansion. Do not add
  prose, multi-line breakdowns, or alternate-reading lists here.
--}}
{{#if content.compressedFrom}}
<p class="trick-compressed-from">
  <span class="trick-compressed-from-label">{{content.compressedFrom.label}}:</span>
  <em class="trick-compressed-from-reading">{{content.compressedFrom.reading}}</em>
</p>
{{/if}}
